    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >终极越野 VR 体验——首次在完全沉浸式 VR 中面对恶劣天气和地形的挑战！为了完成目标，玩家必须克服泥泞危险、水流湍急、道路崎岖等多种难题。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 辆独具特色的全地形汽车——玩家有机会驾驶 8 辆独特的全地形汽车，各自配有运输平板、维修模块、原木栏柱等特色装备，可体验多样游戏风格！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索沉浸式环境——玩家可以在故事模式或自由模式中穿越多元地形，在极端险恶和难以预料的境况中发现新环境。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/88d326bd56b8e2427a83c1741e844683.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/88d326bd56b8e2427a83c1741e844683.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/88d326bd56b8e2427a83c1741e844683.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在驾驶舱实现人车交互——策略性地使用平板电脑、换档杆、雨刷器等设备辅助执行任务。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/771ddbca1f3d514544a46bf2628f3427.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/771ddbca1f3d514544a46bf2628f3427.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/771ddbca1f3d514544a46bf2628f3427.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
